urlText: Caringbah Station Lift 1 between Kingsway and Platform 1/2 is not available
content:
At Caringbah Station Lift 1 between Kingsway and Platform 1/2 is temporarily out of service.
The lift will be closed from Monday 27 February to Sunday 30 April for an upgrade. If you require lift access, use Miranda or Woolooware stations during the closure. Local bus services are also available.
If you need help, ask staff or phone 02 9522 1249.
